'''Sitta taqbaylit''' ('''''Sitta ledanti'''''), tetwasem daɣen '''Sitta n Ledant''', d [[talmest]] n [[afrux|ifrax]] n [[tawacult (tasnudert)|twacult]] n [[Sitta|Sittidae]]. D yiwet sitta s tiddi talemmast, teɣzzif amenni {{aferdis|12|cm}}. Imuren ufella sɛan ini ademdam-azzegzew, imuren imazdaren sɛan ini "taɣaḍt udrar imiwriɣ" yettṛuḥun ɣer ademdam. Awtem yesɛa amgerrad s tawtemt, zdat n tacacit-is d aberkan. Talmest agi d turkidt ; tettečč [[aɣlifḍar|iɣlifḍaren]] deg unebdu, ifsan deg tagrest. Tasemhuyt n ufrurex tettili ɣer mayyu-yunyu. Agdef, yettwebna deg axbuc n ttejṛa (uruz), yesdari asḍar n Kraḍ neɣ kuẓ timellalin, i tsedel tawtemt. Isrifgen ttwaseččen sɣur sin imarawen nsen.

Sitta taqbaylit d talmest tawḥidt n ifrax [[amuɣelaẓri|amuɣel]] n [[Tamurt Taqbaylit|Tmurt Taqbaylit]], anda ur tesegdud kan (tura) kra n tiẓegwa n de [[Tayda|taydiwin]] n ugafa n tmurt. Isem-is ussnan yettak tajmilt i Jean-Paul Ledant, amussan amaswaḍ abiljiki i d-yuffan afrux nni deg waggur {{azmez||tuber|1975}} ; aglam n ufrux yetwexdem sɣur amesnafrux aṛumi [[Jacques Vielliard]]. Isali n tagrut agi yessewhem aṭas amaḍal n tasnafruxt daɣen isali agi yexdem tuzzya n umaḍal (imediaten). Sitta taqbaylit tella taqribt s [[Sitta n Krüper]] (''Sitta krueperi''). Sitta taqbaylit yeqqim-as yiwen kan [[azwu n uzuzer]] (i ufrurex d tudert), yettwaggezen sɣur times, [[arad]] d tigawt talsant ; talmest tettwali dɣa am « [[Umuɣ azegwaɣ n UICN#Talmest deg umihi (EN)|deg umihi]] » sɣur [[Tadukli tagraɣlant i tagaẓt n ugama]].

